Cost of living in <span class="purple_light">Charlotte</span> is 10.92%<span class="green_light"> lower</span> than in <span class="rose_light">Paris</span> <a href="http://www.numbeo.com/cost-of-living/rankings_current.jsp" title="CPI Details" style="float: right; margin-right: 2em; text-align: right"><img src="http://www.numbeo.com/images/information.png" class="image_help" alt="(Info)"></a><span style="margin-top: 0.5em; display: inline-block; width: 100%;"><a href="http://www.numbeo.com/cost-of-living/city_estimator?country=United+States&amp;city=Charlotte%2C+NC" class="discreet_link">Our estimator</a> (with default settings) estimate monthly expenses for a single person at 781.94&#8364; <span class="in_other_currency">(869.59&#36;)</span>
 and for four person family at 2,833.63&#8364; <span class="in_other_currency">(3,151.28&#36;)</span>
 (without rent).</span></div>

