I've lived here my entire life. Beautiful city (in most areas). Nestled right between the mountais (3 hours) and the beach (4 hours). 2nd biggest banking central next to New York. Salaries are high an cost of living is low. Beautiful art scene in NoDa and many areas such as Dilworth and the East area are really up and coming. Plenty of construction going on for better bridges and road systems. Plenty to do. Amusement park right on city limits and 5 malls including a new outlet mall.</div>
